civilization v is easy to get into but takes time to fully master its an addicting combination of empire management and hexbased unit combat the basic premise is that you lead a civilization from its nomadic origins through the ages youll found cities build grand armies and interact with other civilizations over epic games that can span tens of hours the games greatest strength lies in the emergent narratives that you the player will form as you lead your empire to greatness you will love curse and despise your fellow playersai in some ways civilization is indescribable this is one of the gaming experiences you must try at least once in your life i recommend also picking up the expansions gods & kings and brave new world for the most complete experience ps make sure you set aside a few hours for this game because you wont want to play anything else for a while
