welcome to civilization 5 a turnbased strategy game where you are tasked with building the biggest empire and winning the game either by means of science military diplomacy or cultural influence choose the civilization you wish whether thats sending russia to space or having genghis khan become world leader what is good about this is that it is so immersive you can really get stuck into a game and before you know it youre late for work yet while that is fairly undesirable you cant help yourself from advancing into the next era or hold off a few more turns until the wonder youve been working on is completed or even telling yourself youll just keep playing till you win days may fly by but the sense of achievement when you complete a game of civ 5 is overwhelming and makes you just feel pretty good to play the game you will require a quickthinking brain as sometimes the slightest of decisions can result in finding an army on your front door or could leave you at the bottom of the research table to stay afloat you must act fast and establish the means to produce a military quickly should you be attacked but also to keep your research going but dont have too many citizens or your people will become unhappy great strategy game that will be played for years to come definately recommended
