civilization is a fantastic game that i absolutely cant get enough of real time strategy games can become overwhelming at some point which is one reason why i love civilization 5 so much since its turned based the combat system is great lots of technologys to research tons of units to use to crush your enemies diplomacy in singleplayer can get a bit annoying because the ai is so territorial but in multiplayer you can effectively use diplomacy to crush your foes and bring yourself to the top the spy system is both a asset and a disability its a asset since you can get free technologys or convert a citystate to become your ally however it can be a disability since players can see when you steal a technology and most often demand for the removal of your spy and a lot of times the spy fails to get a new technology and gets killed in the process naval combat is insanely fun from trireme rushing your neighbors to a long range naval invasion using battleships and aircraft carriers i would recommend this game to anyone who is a huge fan of strategy turn based games
