this game is an awesome strategy game for people who like to play stuff slow paced in this game you choose a leader for an empirecountry and you have to develop it to have military food for your people your peoples culture scientific discoveries gold and your peoples happiness it may seem overwhelming butbecause of how slowpace the game is it is easy to grasp you can choose to play solo with bots which have many options for their difficulty ranging from just bought the game to pretty much impossible to win because of the bots handicaps < that is just a range of the levels of difficulty not the actual options you can also choose to play with actual people if you do this id recommend the people you play with be a group of friends or just 1 friend because you never really complete the game with strangers sometimes their connection is janky key word their the game doesnt have dedicated servers so lag isnt the games fault or people are just really slow plus you sometimes get kicked when you join a lobby so in my expierence multiplayer isnt worth playing with strangers only a group of or one friend this game really makes the time you invest into it worth it the games last around 10 hours each so playing by yourself on your own time is awesome and you can customize your empire and win through many choices of victories all and all this game is for an avid strategy gamer who likes slow paced games
